videos.headline: Spain: Blackhawks should suspend Keith into postseason
videos.description: The Around the Horn panel reacts to Blackhawks defenseman Duncan Keith being ejected for swinging his stick and catching Wild center Charlie Coyle in the face Tuesday night.
